4d0a0e1d059c85c29f8cd0b","tid":1519081,"uid":156666,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"66f16df37a626a2381d1a3f12e798caa988d1dc0","tid":1519081,"uid":176166,"like":25,"dislike":0,"score":25,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-30T12:42:01.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-30T13:26:09.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>反欺凌<br />\n保護警察兒女 你我有責</strong></span><br />\n＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝<br />\n各位中小學生 為左反欺凌 保護警察兒女<br />\n如果有確鑿證據證明邊位同學老豆老母係警察既話記得要<br />\n1.搵人放佢大頭相上黎<br />\n2.寫埋住邊區<br />\n3.寫埋讀咩學校<br />\n等市民可以隨時留意住佢地有冇比人欺凌 係有需要既時候可以保護佢地<br />\n<br />\n因為欺凌係<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">唔局限係校園</span></span>架<br />\n而家市民咁仇警 有人可能會作出自然反應係街上做小動作搞警察兒女<br />\n例如:<br />\n1.唔小心撞佢出馬路<br />\n2.警察兒女衝紅燈個陣唔小心擋住佢唔比佢上行人路<br />\n3.唔小心踼/撞佢落樓梯<br />\n4.係街拍蚊個陣唔小心打中佢<br />\n5.係巴士唔小心擋住佢唔比佢落車<br />\n6.係巴士/小巴唔小心唔讓開比佢入去靠窗位坐<br />\n7.係巴士/小巴唔小心唔讓開比佢離開個靠窗位<br />\n8.係行人路/過馬路個陣唔小心&quot;KICK&quot;跌佢<br />\n9.唔小心擋住LIP口唔比佢入升降機<br />\n10.警察兒女趕返學搭LIP個陣 唔小心撳哂咁多層<br />\n11.係佢要上車/追車個陣唔小心扮健身撚當街捉住佢扮SALE野唔比佢上車 <br />\n12.係街上唔小心撞佢落花槽<br />\n13.唔小心撞佢部手機落地<br />\n14.唔小心撞佢手上拎住既其他野落地<br />\n15.唔小心倒瀉野食/野飲落佢地件校服到<br />\n16.唔小心倒瀉野食/野飲「入」佢地個書包到<br />\n17.係鋪頭入面唔小心放左啲未比錢既野入佢個袋到<br />\n18.係佢行過個陣唔小心倒屋企啲屎水/污糟水落樓<br />\n19.唔小心打開佢書包拉鍊 等佢啲野跌哂出黎<br />\n20.唔小心放啲蛇蟲鼠蟻入佢書包 <br />\nETC.<br />\n<br />\n大家見到有人咁做既話記得要保護佢地 就算啲警察兒女幾忙幾趕時間都要<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">捉住佢地</span></span>幫佢地報警 <span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">唔好比佢地走</span></span><br />\n你地知香港警察做野幾有效率架啦 一個人日日等幾次39分鐘<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">都唔係好嘥時間姐</span></span><br />\n如果佢地自己打電話想搵人幫手 千祈唔好唔小心轟佢部手機落地然後踢到母雷公咁遠<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1516112/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1516112/page/1</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1516100/page/1?post=2\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1516100/page/1?post=2</a>"},{"pid":"3a881da1628f919316902cf6bcbf2ae40587d7b5","tid":1519081,"uid":267853,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-30T13:29:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/G8JdGq2.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FG8JdGq2.png&h=3722fad1&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"ffeeffe368a2d7a3c1e805e7be7f7977a12bf6d9","tid":1519081,"uid":11845,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-30T13:35:22.000Z","msg":"小心d飛 一個唔覺意就好易墜機嫁<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e809442e383de7a8902d4ab20fbb0ff955b2df06","tid":1519081,"uid":145664,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-30T13:35:32.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">‼️[請幫手加入Twitter 戰線!!!]‼️</span></span><br />\n我哋香港發生嘅每一樣嘢都需要外國人支持<br />\n我哋每晚都要更多人手去推hashtag上treading <br />\n大家快啲入嚟幫手！<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\nTwitter 谷：<br />\n<a href=\"https://t.me/joinchat/M5RkMBax28ZvPIBhVelzag\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fjoinchat%2FM5RkMBax28ZvPIBhVelzag&d=7hybd32tUfzicQL4e%2Fav0g8%2Bx5Wy5jX%2Bp0OgAvZs4CE%3D&h=0d7b0bf8\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/joinchat/M5RkMBax28ZvPIBhVelzag</a><br />\n<br />\n入咗記得睇pinned message同入<br />\n共識台：<br />\n<a href=\"https://t.me/twittermansyunzou\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Ftwittermansyunzou&d=7hybd32tUfzicQL4e%2Fav0g8%2Bx5Wy5jX%2Bp0OgAvZs4CE%3D&h=f19e2b0a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/twittermansyunzou</a><br />\n要做好基本私隱措施 <br />\n因為有狗狗埋伏<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\nWe need you!!"},{"pid":"542a0921ac33e9ce684c9a40b24220d44ae437fc","tid":1519081,"uid":281802,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime